DESCRIPTION:Suitcase carry\, mix in light daily mobility if desired.\n# Suitcase Carry\n\n- Domain: `kettlebells`\n- Session Duration: `~20-25 min`\n- Precedence: `complementary`\n- Frequency: `2-3x/week`\n- Format: `carry`\n- Equipment: `single kettlebell`\n\n## Summary\n\nLoaded carry performed one arm at a time in a suitcase hold\, alternating sides periodically.\n\n## Work\n\n- Carry a single kettlebell for one mile.\n- Use a suitcase hold.\n- Switch arms periodically.\n- Try not to put the bell down.\n- If needed\, perform a single-arm deadlift to switch arms.\n\n## Notes\n\n- Use a kettlebell around 20-30% of body weight.\n- Keep posture tall and controlled throughout the carry.\n
