DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260709
SUMMARY:Hip Mobility
DESCRIPTION:Hip-focused mobility circuit. Use as prep or for recovery.\n# Hip Mobility\n\n- Domain: `mobility`\n- Session Duration: `not specified`\n- Precedence: `complementary`\n- Format: `mobility circuit`\n- Equipment: `bodyweight`\n\n## Summary\n\nHip-focused mobility and activation sequence with gait\, squat\, and balance drills.\n\n## Work\n\n- Hydrants\n- Hip Circles\n- Heel Kicks\n- Straight Leg Kicks (back\, then side)\n- 90/90s\n- Foot roll outs\n- Heel toe walk\n- A Skips\n- C Skips\n- Side Lunges\n- Squat twists\n- Pogos\n- Rotational Bounds\n- Crossovers (Slow/Fasts)\n- Front Squats\n- 90/90s\n- DB Hip Holds\n- Cossack Squats\n- Deadbugs\n- SL Calf Raises\n- Bigeon Reach\n- SL Glute Bridge\n\n## Notes\n\n- Use this as a prep or recovery session for hips and lower body.\n\n## Source\n\n- https://youtube.com/shorts/AIMawvpT0tE?si=FFWj6JcDn5BRQ-Lo\n
END:VEVENT
