SUMMARY:Project 120 - Bands Weekday 2
DESCRIPTION:Second swing-band support session. Can stack with mobility work.\n# Project 120 - Bands Weekday 2\n\n- Domain: `swing-speed`\n- Session Duration: `not specified`\n- Precedence: `complementary`\n- Format: `band work`\n- Equipment: `resistance bands`\n\n## Summary\n\nSecond band-based swing-speed session with position holds and forearm work.\n\n## Work\n\n- 3 x 10 sec holds top of backswing (both sides red band)\n- 3 x 10 sec holds halfway swing (both sides red band)\n- 3 x 10 sec holds impact (both sides red band)\n- 10 x lat pull down reps (red & yellow bands)\n- 3 x 10 second band forearm curls (red strong band)\n- 3 x 10 second band forearm reverse curls (red strong band)\n\n## Notes\n\n- Work both sides where noted.\n\n## Source\n\n- https://membershub.gregsmithgolfcoach.com/hub/eda787ba\n
