SUMMARY:Golf Mobility Warmup
DESCRIPTION:Extended mobility and trunk rotation day. Good as active recovery.\n# Golf Mobility Warmup\n\n- Domain: `mobility`\n- Session Duration: `not specified`\n- Precedence: `complementary`\n- Format: `warmup circuit`\n- Equipment: `bodyweight`\, `optional implements`\n\n## Summary\n\nGolf-specific mobility and prep sequence covering trunk rotation\, locomotion\, and power patterns.\n\n## Work\n\n- Forward Lunges (Overhead\, Side Bend\, Rotation)\n- Glute Bridges (Double\, Single leg)\n- Bird Dogs\n- T-spine Rotations\n- Cat Cow\n- Bear Walk\n- 90/90s\n- Tactical Frogs\n- Half Frogs with Rotation\n- Pushup w/ Downward Dog\n- World's Greatest Stretch\n- X-Factor\n- Lateral Lunge w Rotations\n- Weighted Lateral Lunges\n- Lateral Bounds\n- Rotational Box Jumps\n- KB Carries\n- Single Leg Deadlift\n- Side Planks\n- Kopenhagen Side Planks\n- Med Ball Throws Down\n- Med Ball Chest Pass\n- Cable Pushes\n- Cable Rows\n- Squat Row\n\n## Notes\n\n- Choose the drills that best fit the session or stack them into a longer warmup.\n
END:VEVENT
