SUMMARY:Kettlebell Halos 10 Min
DESCRIPTION:Shoulder health\, control\, and warmup. Can be combined with light mobility.\n# Kettlebell Halos 10 Min\n\n- Domain: `kettlebells`\n- Session Duration: `10 min`\n- Precedence: `complementary`\n- Format: `30 sec on / 30 sec off`\n- Equipment: `kettlebell up to 16 kg`\n\n## Summary\n\nHalo practice focused on smooth control and repeatable reps.\n\n## Work\n\n- Wrestler halos: left - center - right - center - up-and-over - back to start\n\n## Notes\n\n- Count reps and try to beat your best.\n- Keep the movement smooth.\n
END:VEVENT
