SUMMARY:Push Up EMOM 10 Min
DESCRIPTION:Push-up EMOM. Focus on goal rep range.\n# Push Up EMOM 10 Min\n\n- Domain: `bodyweight`\n- Session Duration: `10 min`\n- Precedence: `complementary`\n- Frequency: `2-4x/week`\n- Format: `EMOM`\n- Equipment: `none`\n\n## Summary\n\nProgressive push-up EMOM built around a sustainable rep target that you can repeat every minute for 10 minutes.\n\n## Work\n\n- Pick a push-up number you can complete every minute on the minute for 10 minutes.\n- Example: 5 push-ups per minute for 10 minutes = 50 total push-ups.\n\n## Notes\n\n- Try to increase the rep target every few weeks.\n- Repeat this workout consistently 2-4 times per week.\n
END:VEVENT
